# ── TARA TRAVEL · ENVIRONMENT VARIABLES ───────────────────────────────────────
# Copy this file to .env and fill in your values.
# All services listed here have FREE tiers sufficient for development + testing.

# ── Supabase (FREE — no credit card) ──────────────────────────────────────────
# Create project at https://supabase.com → free tier
# Settings → API → Project URL & anon key
